## Laptop strain: same desktop bundle as workstation, plus battery/power
## management. tlp's power tuning and modes/modectl's CPU-governor switching
## are complementary, not redundant -- tlp handles fine-grained
## battery-charge/USB-autosuspend/etc. that distro-modectl's per-mode
## governor switch doesn't touch.
ubuntu-desktop-minimal
flatpak
gnome-shell-extensions
gnome-tweaks
gamemode
mangohud
winetricks
tlp
tlp-rdw
